element.name: Speedway by Donnacha, Traditional Cache (3/2)

long-description.p: Cache is located in a small forest in Delgany, Co. Wicklow. I mountain bike up here all the time, so bring your bike if you're up for it. Parking available at N53 08.822 W006 06.322. Start at the end of the car park and take the track to the left, and follow to the top.

center.font: Visit the Geocaching Ireland discussion forum HERE

element.encoded-hints: As you come to the end of the rocks while walking towards the coast, there are two tress on your left. Behind one of the trees is an evergreen tree. Cache is at the base of the tree on the forest side.
